-> Meta Charset is what determines how text is transmitted and stored. This text data is usually converted to binary first and then there needs to be a kind of cipher that connects characters with their correct binary equivalents.

-> ExifTool is a free and open source software program which is used to read, write and update metadata of various types of files such as PDF, Audio, Video and images.

-> meta-data = a set of data that describes and gives information about other data.
